item.title: Prayer bpn13010 in Nalik
item.description: Tamon a mun saan di yaalaxaaf di na paazaai be wan a Nakmai? Fakilaan: a vavisfaaruing kun a Nakmai! Naan be a Nakmai! Naande a mun yaanakilaaing Sina, ma di nat falos a vaartulaaiing Sina! (Source category: A Vaaroving kun a Zaan di Yaalaxaaf (Remover of Difficulties)) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13010)
